OpenOSPFD - Why?

Main problems
Link-state protocols are complex
The database on all routers need to be in sync or you are doomed.
Large networks tend to get unstable with some implementations
Interoperability is a nightmare
RFC is imprecise

Developing OpenOSPFD is a challange

